      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "## ⚠ Breaking change\n\n`${originalname}` persistence has been **removed**. `${originalname}` may now only be used as the **sole value** of *Attachment Format*; combining it with other text or variables (e.g. `IMG-${originalname}`, `${originalname}-${date}`) is rejected by the settings validator with an inline error.\n\n**Migration:** if your previous *Attachment Format* combined `${originalname}` with other parts, change it to either a plain `${originalname}` (to keep the original filename verbatim) or a format that does not reference `${originalname}`. `originalNameStorage` entries in `data.json` are no longer read and can be deleted manually. The `Clear unused original name storage` command was also removed. See the README's [Original Name](https://github.com/trganda/obsidian-attachment-management#original-name) section for details.\n\n## Highlights\n\n- **Settings validator** for *Attachment Format* — empty values, illegal filename characters (`\\ / : * ? \" < > |`), unknown `${...}` placeholders, and mixed `${originalname}` are flagged inline and refused on save.\n- **ConfirmModal refresh** — warning icon, paragraph-styled message, destructive-styled action button, tighter async error handling.\n- **Cursor-jump fix** when pasting an image (#205).\n- **`isAttachment` API fix** — a latent crash when called with a string path (`this.app` referenced from a free function).\n- **Resolved several uninitialized-property TS errors** in the plugin class.\n\n## Build & supply-chain\n\n- **Dev toolchain upgraded** — TypeScript 5.9, Prettier 3, ESLint 9 flat config, typescript-eslint 8, `commit-and-tag-version` replacing the deprecated `standard-version`.\n- **`pnpm.overrides`** added to patch all transitive CVEs; `pnpm audit` now reports **0 vulnerabilities** (was 24).\n- **Release workflow migrated to pnpm** with `--frozen-lockfile` and a setup-node pnpm cache (#211).\n- **SLSA v1.0 build provenance** is now generated for every release asset via `actions/attest-build-provenance@v4`. Verify with:\n  ```\n  gh attestation verify main.js --owner trganda\n  ```\n\n## Pull requests in this release\n\n- #205 — fix: prevent cursor jumping to top after pasting image\n- #209 — feat: remove original-storage support and add attachment-format validator\n- #211 — ci: switch release workflow to pnpm and add SLSA provenance\n\n[Full diff: 0.10.0...0.11.0](https://github.com/trganda/obsidian-attachment-management/compare/0.10.0...0.11.0) · [CHANGELOG.md](https://github.com/trganda/obsidian-attachment-management/blob/main/CHANGELOG.md)",
